<br>
I will say that in the end game, the robe has had virtually no  use...mine stays bagged.  Mana is not a problem for the average raid Wizard that has a number of buffs available.  Even so, I'm sure there are lots of Wizards that could make use of this robe even today.  It is unfortunate that it was taken out of the game without any comment at all regarding why.<br>
